const Orders = (props) => {
  return (
    <svg
      className={props.className}
      id="box"
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      width="18"
      height="16"
      viewBox="0 0 22 20"
    >
      <path
        id="Path_157"
        data-name="Path 157"
        d="M10,12a1,1,0,0,0,0,2h4a1,1,0,0,0,0-2Z"
        transform="translate(-1 -2)"
      />
      <path
        id="Path_158"
        data-name="Path 158"
        d="M4,2A3,3,0,0,0,1,5V19a3,3,0,0,0,3,3H20a3,3,0,0,0,3-3V5a3,3,0,0,0-3-3ZM20,4H4A1,1,0,0,0,3,5V8H21V5A1,1,0,0,0,20,4ZM3,19V10H21v9a1,1,0,0,1-1,1H4A1,1,0,0,1,3,19Z"
        transform="translate(-1 -2)"
        fill-rule="evenodd"
      />
    </svg>
  );
};

export default Orders;
